Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B ,
Happy Thursday!
One of the best parts of writing Not Boring is that I get to send out a bat=
 signal about the things I=E2=80=99m interested in and exploring, and then =
a bunch of smart people share their thoughts and recommendations.=20
When I wrote Bill-a-Bear [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMuOhCAQRb9G=
dm3kJbpgMZv5DVNAaZNGMIhj_Puh22QmqUdSlaqbeywUXFK-9Jb2Qt5lKteGOuK5BywFMzl2zJN=
