eAtbbnlYAc7s9katMrVHK0xho2KCSOgEd26sHY_zF7AvurflWT9p1PXryesGD6L6nCqfT2iL9eE=
EUxAd5svN8MPjmnBiLmydROUNzlGGVeyVnWbrXR4P3aU9T2pyi7Vq_gv-gvGu4lY] in Januar=
y, and mentioned my displeasure with bill.com, a couple things happened. Fi=
rst, a bunch of people replied saying that I should check out Melio. Second=
, Melio=E2=80=99s co-founder and CEO, Matan Bar [https://email.mg2.substack=
=2Ecom/c/eJxFkM2OhCAQhJ9mOBpoBPXAYS_zGoa=
f1iGjYLDdiW-_OB42gSakUhT1eUs453KaLe_E=
rjHSuaFJ-NkXJMLCjh3LGIMRGnqp2oEF0wbRq57FfZwK4mrjYqgcyLbDLdFbijl9HZyDYi-jhZq=
qQyN0QxcGDzaIQfHQ-1ZXpb9z7REiJo8Gf7GcOSFbzIto2x_y5wHPuugTrx81Pq_1tlqyydnCog=
