nd pick off customers.</strong></em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: #1a=
1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">After writing=
 that piece, I got two types of responses, from two groups of people:</p><o=
l style=3D"margin: 1em 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-=
special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0;"><strong>Founders and Small Business Owners</stron=
g>. This group strongly agreed with me. They, too, struggled to figure out =
bill.com&#8217;s product, and they had businesses to run. They shared my dr=
ead of logging into bill.com.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px =
